    "body": "### Problem\n\nfunctions in treesitter are differentiated between the `@function` group for function definitions like `fun foo(x) print(x) end`, and `@function.call` for calling functions e.g. `foo(5)`. `@constructor` conflates both.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nideally there should be a `@constructor.call` group to explicitly capture this.",
